monsters.name: Darkness Stirs
monsters.description: A strange energy emanates from the depths. The Arcane Synthesizer has begun its work, and twisted creatures emerge from the shadows.

monsters.name: Corruption Awakens
monsters.description: The Arcane Synthesizer pulses with dark energy. All players loose 2 barriers, and gain 1 Arcane Droplet.

monsters.name: Abyssal Alchemist
monsters.description: The Abyssal Alchemist appears. For only this next navigation, players may go to this location, and trade 2 Arcane Droplets or ALL your barriers for 1 of any Rune from the supply. No combat may take place here.

monsters.name: Abyss Tragedy
monsters.description: The Arcane Creation explodes, injuring all players in the abyss. All players in the abyss loose 4 barriers, but gain 2 Arcane Droplets.
